title: Brian Jenkins is pleased with the Hornets 1st Win
text:
Brian Jenkins is pleased with the Hornets 1st Win Tools By Alabama News Network 
Story Created: Sep 29, 2015 at 10:48 PM CDT 
Alabama State picked up their first win of the season and in the process Head Coach picked up his first win as the Hornets head coach as ASU defeated Mississippi Valley State 45-15. "Our guys came out and played, they played physical and we executed early," Head Coach said. "I'll tell you what Mississippi Valley is headed in the right direction. They were a tough, physical football team and we had to earn everything ."
